<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Partnership Request Update</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: #10b981; color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
    .content { background: #ffffff; padding: 30px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-top: none; }
    .footer { background: #f9fafb; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; }
    .status-badge { display: inline-block; padding: 6px 12px; border-radius: 20px; font-weight: bold; margin: 10px 5px; }
    .status-approved { background: #d1fae5; color: #065f46; }
    .status-rejected { background: #fee2e2; color: #991b1b; }
    .status-review { background: #fef3c7; color: #92400e; }
    .info-box { background: #f0fdf4; border-left: 4px solid #10b981; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; }
    h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 24px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>ðŸ“¢ Status Update</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <p>Dear <strong>{{pocName}}</strong>,</p>
      
      <p>There has been an update to your partnership request:</p>
      
      <div class="info-box">
        <p><strong>Reference ID:</strong> {{requestId}}</p>
        <p><strong>Event Title:</strong> {{eventTitle}}</p>
        <p><strong>Previous Status:</strong> <span class="status-badge">{{oldStatus}}</span></p>
        <p><strong>New Status:</strong> <span class="status-badge">{{newStatus}}</span></p>
      </div>
      
      {{#if comment}}
      <p><strong>Message from ALX Team:</strong></p>
      <blockquote style="border-left: 3px solid #d1d5db; padding-left: 15px; color: #6b7280; font-style: italic;">
        {{comment}}
      </blockquote>
      {{/if}}
      
      <p>If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to reach out.</p>
      
      <p>Best regards,<br><strong>The ALX Partnership Team</strong></p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{current_year}} ALX Africa. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
